title: Go Beyond Invisible Walls | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Go Beyond Invisible Walls | Joel Osteen
description:
If we only associate with people that are like us, we’ll miss out on what God wants to do in our lives. He can use the people you least expect to move you toward your destiny.

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
